These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, broccoli, lemon, papaya
1. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
3. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | strawberry | broccoli | lemon | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, almond-milk, tea
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola | tea | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, sudoku, writing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | writing | sudoku | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, crime, fantasy, time-travel
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | epic | time-travel | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
