.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, blueberry, artichoke, lettuce
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating lettuce##2
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | lettuce | blueberry | pineapple | artichoke |

