1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | hedgehog | dog | bird | frog |

