.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, ambient, gospel, pop
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | ambient | funk | pop |

 